item.title: Training p2p runescape
item.dc:creator: @Berky-Scape Berky-Scape
item.description:
@Berky-Scape wrote:

I should suggest:
Yaks - Neitiznot
Green dragons - Wilderniss (This is just random I know you don’t wan’t them but for others maybe)
Blue Dragons - Taverly Dungeon
Lesser demons - Karamja Dungeon
Rock crabs - Relekka
Giant Rock crabs - Choas tunnel
Druids - Taverly
Gorilla’s - Ape atol
Soul wars - Edgeville (It is a waste of time trust me)
Pest Control - Port Sarim (It was good a long while ago, but you still can use it)
Scorpions - Falador mines (You also help the people that are mining there ;))
Guards - Ardougne
Khazard - They way up yo Ardougne
Ogres - Near Castle Wars (Bring a rope, would be handy)
Slayer monsters near your level
Cockroaches - Edgeville dungeon
Hill Giants - Varrock dungeon
Ice Trolls - Neitiznot
Aviansies - God Wars Dungeon
Bandos minions like Goblins - God wars Dungeon
